{"tid":435924,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[OnTV直播] 港超聯 15/10 - 14:30 - 流浪 vs RF富力","createTime":"2017-10-14T16:54:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-15T03:35:30.000Z","uid":9030,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0479d927d9211f235cc4c23f45cf1c4e611500b2","tid":435924,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T16:54:48.000Z","msg":"視像直播Link：<br />\n手機版 <a href=\"http://tv.on.cc/mlive/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftv.on.cc%2Fmlive%2F&d=3kdSw36gXA8gdioUiDeTTJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=591225b2\" target=\"_blank\">http://tv.on.cc/mlive/</a>　　　　　　　　 　<br />\n網頁版 <a href=\"http://tv.on.cc/live/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftv.on.cc%2Flive%2F&d=3kdSw36gXA8gdioUiDeTTJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=f00fc07f\" target=\"_blank\">http://tv.on.cc/live/</a>　<br />\n<br />\n15/10<br />\n14:30 - 流浪 vs R&amp;F富力 @深水埗運動場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20171015/photo/bkn-20171015000519686-1015_00882_001_01b.jpg?20171015000533\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20171015%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171015000519686-1015_00882_001_01b.jpg%3F20171015000533&h=f4429b35&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e8808caca910d5f57d395e4c488d875fec276878","tid":435924,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T16:55:07.000Z","msg":"預計雙方正選陣容<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>流浪</strong></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">黃子揚<br />\n徐宏傑 摩域治 基頓 楊賜麟<br />\n黎洛賢 卡拉鍚 廖培楓<br />\n鄭兆均 基士頓 卓耀國</div><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: navy;\">R&amp;F富力</span></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">般連奴<br />\n基奧雲尼 伊達 楊子藝<br />\n勞烈斯 侯俊杰<br />\n梁永豐 趙銘 羅拔圖 曾健晃<br />\n周煜辰</div><br />\n<br />\n停賽: /<br />\n受傷: /"},{"pid":"87e478e2fd36a494c86a4aec0a7209081b40ed07","tid":435924,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T16:55:17.000Z","msg":"兩軍情報:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>流浪</strong></span><br />\n標準流浪雖然在高級銀牌賽淘汰夢想FC進身8強，但今季聯賽卻告連輸3場，當中兩場僅以1比2和0比1不敵冠忠南區及陽光元朗。然而，主教練狄恩對球隊前景仍感樂觀，並寄語球員只要將平時操練所做的帶到比賽上，便離勝利不遠。<br />\n狄恩說：「其實球隊大部分賽事，戰況都處於均勢，球員經常在上下半場臨完結前失去集中力，導致失球，之後就很難收復失地。老實說，這兩個月以來，我對球員並沒有不滿，他們亦在操練期間非常落力，所以他們要做的，就是將平時在操練所做的，在比賽中展現出來。始終賽果才是最重要的，我認為球隊前3場聯賽值得最少取得1或2分，但有時足球就是這樣殘酷。不過，相信只要有好的發揮，從之前的錯誤中學習，在打開勝利之門後，就會更容易重返正軌。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: navy;\">R&amp;F富力</span></strong><br />\n由於主場及天雨的問題，R&amp;F富力先後有兩場聯賽賽事延期，目前在聯賽僅踢兩場，先後不敵香港飛馬及冠忠南區，於高級銀牌賽首圈亦遭理文淘汰出局。主帥馬里科坦言球隊不適應「港式足球」，並會就之前的比賽進行分析，亦不排除改變踢法，並以長傳、斬中及射門的方式來爭取入球。"},{"pid":"c7be7061dd7d934d3a82102e744aebe62ed10b40","tid":435924,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T16:55:36.000Z","msg":"港超積分榜<br />\n1\t傑志\t4賽10分 +9<br />\n2\t飛馬\t4賽10分 +3<br />\n3\t南區\t5賽9分 +3<br />\n4\t大埔 5賽8分 +4<br />\n5\t夢想FC 4賽7分 -3<br />\n6\t元朗\t4賽6分 -3<br />\n7\t理文\t3賽4分 0<br />\n8\t<strong><span style=\"color: navy;\">R&amp;F富力 2賽0分 -3</span></strong><br />\n9\t東方龍獅\t4賽0分 -5<br />\n10\t<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>流浪 3賽0分 -1</strong></span>"},{"pid":"a8e946ea47478bd6d811fc0d1dec5af1ff0594e8","tid":435924,"uid":9030,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T16:55:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> = 支持<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>流浪</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> = 支持<strong><span style=\"color: navy;\">R&amp;F富力</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nlike呢個留言 = 支持 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>兩隊欖炒</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ea660e92acd1a7629abb787bae7a5678cf336ea","tid":435924,"uid":4635,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T16:57:08.000Z","msg":"並不排除以射門方式爭取入球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"876bfd6165c89319236d487f70cbc59b0c978387","tid":435924,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T16:58:03.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">比賽開始前5小時內，天文台發出以下警告訊號(或仍然生效)或預計將會發出以下警告訊號<span style=\"color: red;\">賽事會取消</span><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n- 八號或更高颱風訊號 或 黑色暴雨警告訊號</span></strong>"},{"pid":"0b4199d811610a9d94f4bf32b77f2741d212a9f9","tid":435924,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T16:59:28.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">比賽開始前5小時內，天文台發出以下警告訊號(或仍然生效)或預計將會發出以下警告訊號, <span style=\"color: red;\">將按既定程序於賽前視察比賽場地，檢查並確認場地是否適合如常進行比賽</span><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n- 三號或以下颱風訊號 或 紅色或黃色暴雨警告訊號</span></strong>"},{"pid":"75c5148ac0c7cbe5d698d98d8cf64b8e6bb0cec5","tid":435924,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T17:07:49.000Z","msg":"其實都幾大機會cancel"},{"pid":"04770ecf0c0852641daa968dbcf7e8f826a50d08","tid":435924,"uid":2883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T17:17:11.000Z","msg":"垃隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"281e0dfffb044ddd6fee1990a4a44954f403b725","tid":435924,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T00:46:37.000Z","msg":"9:30仲掛緊8號就會cancel"},{"pid":"98971e125aa0df3bc5abf0ebb530447df78a19b3","tid":435924,"uid":33053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T00:53:19.000Z","msg":"個風又玩鳩畜力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"472e1bdc1b28aa68d1c32d0f19eac4f65aa06af0","tid":435924,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T03:35:30.000Z","msg":"香港足總宣布：於10月15日下午2時30分假深水埗運動場舉行之香港超級聯賽 - 標準流浪 對 R&amp;F富力 之賽事，鍳於在比賽開始前五小時內，八號颱風訊號仍然生效，故賽事取消，補賽安排將會在稍後公佈。"}]}